views/states

main state/home page
	-list of product categories and featured products and shop all categories option

category page
	-list all products for a selected category
	-filters sidebar

product page
	-product info
	-reviews
	-add a review
		-only available to logged in users
	-low stock warning "BUY NOW!"
	-add to cart
	-similar products
	ADMINS
		-edit reviews
		-edit product
		-edit categories
		-edit availability
		-"Currently Unavailable" if out of stock, page does not show on all products, only accessible via direct url or past order

shopping cart
	-items in cart, with editable amount
	-checkout button
	-promo code

payment
	-enter payment info
	-submit cart to order

order history
	-past orders with products, price, status

ADMIN
	order management
		-view all orders, sortable by status
		-ability to change order status
		-view details of specific order (take admin to order page, with extra admin functionality)

	user managementgit 
		-edit user status to admin
		-delete a user
		-trigger password reset

login/signup
	-facebook and google, or local


